body: Aww, right. We could still hide the op, then switch to V2 in a couple of weeks. @yongtang if you're up for it, you'd need to change https://www.github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/python/ops/hidden_ops.txt#L159 and write a wrapper like this: http://google3/third_party/tensorflow/python/ops/image_ops_impl.py?l=925
